# Documentation Rules

Full spec: `00_system/documentation_rules.md`

## Naming

- Slugs: hyphens, lowercase (`track-slug`)
- Drafts: `lyrics_vN.md`, `suno_prompt_vN.md`, `cover_prompt_vN.md`
- Finals: `lyrics_final.md`, `final_suno_fields.md`, `final_style.md`

No `notes2.md`, `final_final.md`.

## Writing

- One source of truth per fact — link, don't duplicate.
- Warm but structured — e.g. *"Run 4 had the body; vocal still theatrical — lower weirdness on retry."*
- Learning entries: context, observation, action, scope, type (see `04_templates/learning_entry_template.md`).

## Agent checklist after sessions

- [ ] Status fields and `track_map.md` match reality
- [ ] New versions numbered, not overwritten
- [ ] Listening notes linked to audio filename
- [ ] Reusable patterns → `03_global_learnings/`
- [ ] No artist names added to SUNO prompts
